title: Walgreens
description: Walgreens, a prominent brand in the retail pharmacy industry, is known for its distinctive color palette. The brand's colors include a vibrant red (E31837), a warm orange (F37520), a calming blue (489CD4), a deeper shade of blue (2774A6), and a neutral grey (35393D). These colors are officially sourced from Walgreens' API Integration and Marketing Style Guide.
